                     <interp inst="t18321018-212-person1851" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a pawnbroker. The prisoner pawned these two reams of paper with me on the 11th of August.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18321018-212-person1852">
                  MORRIS 
                  SALMON
               <interp inst="t18321018-212-person1852" type="surname" value="SALMON"></interp>
