                     <interp inst="t18321018-212-person1852" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am one of the firm of Salmon, Cunningham, and Co. The prisoner lived in our employ as <rs id="t18321018-212-viclabel1183" type="occupation">porter</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18321018-212-victim1849 t18321018-212-viclabel1183"></join>, and left us in July last - I did not send this order to the prosecutors', nor give any direction; I have no doubt this is forged.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18321018-212-person1853">
                  JOHN 
                  CUNNINGHAM
